    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "Rusting ammunition is made using a ore louse's saliva and, when activated, deals damage to objects or creatures primarily made of metal. The target takes persistent damage for a duration determined by the type of ammunition used. A creature that drops to 0 Hit Points while taking this persistent damage crumbles into fine powder; its gear remains. The ammunition's type determines the maximum amount of an object that's destroyed.",
